headline: GTA Online
subtitle: This Week on the Podium: The Vapid GB200
content: Stop by the lobby of the Diamond Casino & Resort any time this week to give the Lucky Wheel a spin. Who knows, you could walk away with GTA$, RP, snacks, clothing, not to mention a Vapid GB200, a no-frills, two-door rally-car that harkens back to an era of reckless abandon.
